# Embedded SPA bundle (internal/spa/dist). The real `npm run build` emits
# index.html + hashed assets here; only the committed PLACEHOLDER index.html is
# tracked so `go build ./...` + the //go:embed compile on a fresh checkout with
# no node step (mirroring how gen/ is handled — but committed, not an artifact).
# The real built index.html overwrites the placeholder locally/in CI; git keeps
# the placeholder version. The hashed assets/ are build output, never tracked.
/internal/spa/dist/*
!/internal/spa/dist/index.html

# local agent tooling artifact (not project code)
.claude-flow/
